357
00:21:50,390 --> 00:21:51,558
Dia sudah gila.

358
00:21:51,641 --> 00:21:53,435
Temanmu juga selamat makan.

359
00:21:53,810 --> 00:21:57,022
Aku yakin orang itu
bukan orang yang kabur tadi.

360
00:21:57,606 --> 00:22:01,234
Tapi pria tinggi itu katanya
datang sendiri, ternyata berlima.

361
00:22:01,318 --> 00:22:03,153
Kau <i>rapper</i>?

362
00:22:03,236 --> 00:22:04,279
Ayo jalan.

363
00:22:08,742 --> 00:22:10,660
- Eun-sup.
- Bukan. Aku Yeong.

364
00:22:10,744 --> 00:22:12,579
Bukan. Kau Eun-sup.

365
00:22:12,913 --> 00:22:14,289
Tadi kau dia.

366
00:22:15,207 --> 00:22:16,458
Yeong tidak akan...

367
00:22:18,335 --> 00:22:19,503
Bodoh? Tak mungkin.

368
00:22:20,128 --> 00:22:20,962
Yeong tahu

369
00:22:21,046 --> 00:22:22,589
