00:26:46,186 --> 00:26:47,979
Dilarang merayu sebelum makan.

446
00:26:49,355 --> 00:26:51,065
Syukurlah tak ada apa-apa. Aku pergi.

447
00:26:54,027 --> 00:26:55,528
<i>Pada saat ini juga</i>

448
00:26:56,529 --> 00:26:58,907
