472
00:28:46,867 --> 00:28:47,952
<i>Sepertinya wanita.</i>

473
00:28:55,793 --> 00:28:58,087
Jangan kabur. Kau sudah mau lari!

474
00:29:01,298 --> 00:29:02,841
<i>Wajah Myeong Seung-a.</i>

475
00:29:03,425 --> 00:29:05,010
<i>Siapa dia?</i>

476
00:29:05,344 --> 00:29:08,263
Bukankah seharusnya kau di kantor polisi?

477
00:29:10,641 --> 00:29:12,059
Tapi bajumu...

478
00:29:13,644 --> 00:29:15,145
Kau mau berkencan?

479
00:29:16,689 --> 00:29:18,107
Maaf.

480
00:29:19,149 --> 00:29:20,317
Kau habis melayat?

481
00:29:22,236 --> 00:29:23,195
Rambutmu rapi.

482
00:29:24,947 --> 00:29:26,615
<i>Aku tak boleh menarik perhatian.</i>

483
00:29:34,081 --> 00:29:36,000
Kau panggil aku?

484
00:29:37,001 --> 00:29:38,043
Dengan jarimu?

485
00:29:39,128 --> 00:29:40,379
Dia sudah gila.

486
00:29:46,260 --> 00:29:47,886
Kau mati jika hal ini tak penting.

487
00:29:50,180 --> 00:29:51,306
<i>Dia kuat.</i>

488
00:29:52,099 --> 00:29:53,350
<i>Hanya ada satu cara.</i>

489
00:30:01,817 --> 00:30:03,193
Ada yang ingin kutahu.

490
00:30:08,032 --> 00:30:09,324
Apa aku menyukaimu?

491
00:30:09,616 --> 00:30:11,035
Atau kau yang menyukaiku?

492
00:30:12,286 --> 00:30:13,287
Di dunia ini.

493
00:30:17,166 --> 00:30:18,917
Pantas kau tak punya pacar.

494
00:30:19,334 --> 00:30:20,377
Jangan begitu.

495
00:30:21,211 --> 00:30:22,796
Apa itu di wajahmu? Rumput laut?

496
00:30:22,880 --> 00:30:23,714
Jangan dihapus...

497
00:30:24,673 --> 00:30:26,675
Apa? Bisa bermasalah.

498
00:30:26,884 --> 00:30:28,594
Aku sudah buat <i>japchae</i>. Ambil nanti.

499
00:30:39,021 --> 00:30:40,439
Jika aku bisa bertarung...

500
00:30:40,522 --> 00:30:42,649
Aku sebenarnya bisa.

501
00:30:42,733 --> 00:30:43,567
Satu, dua...

502
00:30:49,573 --> 00:30:52,451
Kau mengagetkanku. Ada apa denganmu?

503
00:30:52,534 --> 00:30:54,828
Tae-eul bilang kau
hanya bisa keluar malam hari...

504
00:30:54,912 --> 00:30:57,331
Siapa wanita ini? Dia cantik...

505
00:30:57,414 --> 00:30:59,458
Jo Yeong. Benar-benar dia. Luar biasa.

506
00:30:59,541 --> 00:31:01,168
- Matanya sangat cantik.
- Na-ri.

507
00:31:01,251 --> 00:31:03,003
- Naik mobil <i>sport</i>.
- Myeong Na-ri.

508
00:31:04,213 --> 00:31:05,756
Kau bertemu Na-ri?

509
00:31:06,173 --> 00:31:08,217
Kalian bicara apa? Beri tahu aku.

510
00:31:08,300 --> 00:31:09,885
Katanya mau buat masalah denganmu

511
00:31:10,719 --> 00:31:11,929
dan disuruh ambil <i>japchae.</i>

512
00:31:14,223 --> 00:31:16,892
<i>Japchae</i>? Masalah? Denganku?

513
00:31:18,685 --> 00:31:20,395
Jelaskan dengan benar.

514
00:31:20,479 --> 00:31:22,189
Sebelum itu kau bicara apa?

515
00:31:22,272 --> 00:31:23,524
Kenapa tiba-tiba <i>japchae</i>?

516
00:31:23,607 --> 00:31:25,734
- Kau suka dia?
- Tentu saja!

517
00:31:28,153 --> 00:31:30,697
Aku tak bisa pergi sekarang.

518
00:31:31,198 --> 00:31:33,575
Telepon dan bilang aku
akan ke sana lain kali.

519
00:31:33,659 --> 00:31:34,785
Aku tenangkan diri dulu.

520
00:31:35,786 --> 00:31:37,830
Ini <i>japchae</i> pertama kami.

521
00:31:38,956 --> 00:31:39,873
Kau menyedihkan.

522
00:31:40,082 --> 00:31:42,292
Berapa lama? Sepuluh menit cukup?

523
00:31:43,669 --> 00:31:44,670
Seratus tahun!

524
00:31:44,962 --> 00:31:45,963
Menyebalkan.

525
00:31:55,764 --> 00:31:56,723
Kau kembali?

526
00:31:56,807 --> 00:31:58,142
Ya. Ada yang baru?

527
00:31:59,726 --> 00:32:00,602
Tak ada.

528
00:32:05,649 --> 00:32:06,483
Enak sekali.

529
00:32:07,067 --> 00:32:09,027
Kau pandai memilih kimchi.

530
00:32:13,282 --> 00:32:14,324
Apa itu semua?

531
00:32:15,659 --> 00:32:18,287
Detektif Shim bilang itu diperlukan
untuk mengintai.

532
00:32:19,913 --> 00:32:21,248
Kau mau berkemah?

533
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:26,044
Ada apa dengan Sin-jae?

534
00:32:26,420 --> 00:32:27,880
Kenapa dia tukar jadwal?

535
00:32:28,046 --> 00:32:29,006
Aku tak tanya.

536
00:32:30,174 --> 00:32:31,884
Jika dia mau bicara,

537
00:32:31,967 --> 00:32:33,886
pasti dia sudah bicara sebelum ditanya.

538
00:32:35,888 --> 00:32:38,807
Bagus. Maka itu aku juga tak tanya.

539
00:32:45,272 --> 00:32:46,148
Kenapa?

540
00:32:47,065 --> 00:32:49,985
Kau jatuh cinta dengan kepintaranku?

541
00:32:50,068 --> 00:32:51,111
Bukan itu.

542
00:32:51,403 --> 00:32:54,823
Barang apa yang kau pakai
di bibir dan wajahmu itu?

543
00:32:57,618 --> 00:32:59,536
Pepatah lama selalu benar.

544
00:33:00,662 --> 00:33:03,332
Tak bisa pakai <i>lip balm</i> serbaguna
di depan teman.

545
00:33:04,208 --> 00:33:05,083
Buatmu saja.

546
00:33:05,167 --> 00:33:06,460
Satu bisa untuk semua.

547
00:33:08,754 --> 00:33:09,671
Terima kasih.

548
00:33:10,589 --> 00:33:11,423
Astaga.

549
00:33:14,301 --> 00:33:16,053
Kau yakin Park Jung-gu tak pulang?

550
00:33:16,637 --> 00:33:18,055
Ya. Sudah kupastikan.

551
00:33:18,722 --> 00:33:19,598
Baiklah.

552
00:33:20,265 --> 00:33:21,141
Bagus.

553
00:33:22,559 --> 00:33:24,603
Tapi, korbannya...

554
00:33:26,271 --> 00:33:29,608
Dia pasti tak tahu
jika akan mati begitu, 'kan?

555
00:33:33,779 --> 00:33:34,655
Jangmi.

556
00:33:35,989 --> 00:33:38,200
Kau baru pertama tangani kasus pembunuhan?

557
00:33:38,909 --> 00:33:39,743
Ya.

558
00:33:40,327 --> 00:33:42,037
Kau tahu banyak polisi bunuh diri?

559
00:33:42,663 --> 00:33:43,538
Apa?

560
00:33:43,622 --> 00:33:46,333
Kasus seperti ini akan banyak ke depannya.

561
00:33:47,209 --> 00:33:48,126
Ini pekerjaan kita.

562
00:33:49,294 --> 00:33:51,338
Kita harus menyelidiki sekuat tenaga,

563
00:33:52,172 --> 00:33:56,468
dan jika kasus selesai,
harus melupakannya sekuat tenaga juga.

564
00:33:57,344 --> 00:33:59,221
Jika tak begitu, kau bisa cepat berhenti.

565
00:34:00,639 --> 00:34:01,515
Baik.

566
00:34:04,101 --> 00:34:06,436
Kita harus apa jika mau kasus selesai?

567
00:34:07,354 --> 00:34:08,939
Harus tangkap pelakunya, 'kan?

568
00:34:10,023 --> 00:34:11,942
- Ya.
- Maka, perhatikan yang benar.

569
00:34:13,026 --> 00:34:14,152
Baik.

570
00:34:17,739 --> 00:34:19,658
Itu dia, Park Jung-gu.

571
00:34:20,492 --> 00:34:21,868
Jangmi, ayo turun.

572
00:34:24,913 --> 00:34:25,789
Pak Park Jung-gu?

573
00:34:25,872 --> 00:34:27,040
Sial.

574
00:34:35,132 --> 00:34:36,425
Astaga.

575
00:34:43,140 --> 00:34:44,766
Tae-eul! Sudah aku tangkap.

576
00:34:48,645 --> 00:34:50,397
Sepertinya aku tangkap pelakunya.

577
00:34:51,398 --> 00:34:52,274
Baiklah.

578
00:34:56,028 --> 00:34:58,697
Tapi sepertinya dia tak bernapas.

579
00:34:59,906 --> 00:35:02,451
Tak bisa. Borgolnya hanya satu.

580
00:35:05,245 --> 00:35:06,455
Pak Park Jung-gu.

581
00:35:07,497 --> 00:35:08,790
Bangunlah.

582
00:35:09,041 --> 00:35:10,584
<i>Jangmi menangkap Park Jung-gu.</i>

583
00:35:11,793 --> 00:35:13,795
Pak Park Jung-gu!

584
00:35:13,879 --> 00:35:15,547
<i>Aku baru saja sampai rumah.</i>

585
00:35:16,298 --> 00:35:18,008
<i>Aku akan ke sana.</i>

586
00:35:18,091 --> 00:35:20,302
Tae-eul, dia tak bernapas...

587
00:35:20,385 --> 00:35:21,678
Aku harus apa?

588
00:35:22,220 --> 00:35:25,140
<i>Sin-jae, jangan pura-pura tak baca.</i>

589
00:35:25,515 --> 00:35:26,350
Pak Park Jung-gu!

590
00:35:43,158 --> 00:35:44,993
Banyak pelanggan, ya.

591
00:35:47,454 --> 00:35:48,580
Ibu.

592
00:35:50,290 --> 00:35:51,500
Apa itu menyenangkan?

593
00:35:55,962 --> 00:35:56,922
Maafkan ibu.

594
00:35:58,590 --> 00:36:00,050
Ibu tak akan ulangi lagi.

595
00:36:01,676 --> 00:36:04,346
Saat ibu duduk di sini,
ibu rasa semua akan baik-baik saja.

596
00:36:05,180 --> 00:36:08,058
Ibu jadi tak memikirkan hal lain.

597
00:36:10,602 --> 00:36:13,814
Sekarang ibu tak bisa judi
karena tak ada uang.

598
00:36:17,150 --> 00:36:19,444
Kau sakit dalam waktu yang lama.

599
00:36:21,363 --> 00:36:22,864
Sesudah kau sadar,

600
00:36:23,657 --> 00:36:25,492
rasanya ibu punya segalanya.

601
00:36:25,784 --> 00:36:28,954
Ibu pikir kita akan bahagia,
tapi tiba-tiba ayahmu jadi begitu.

602
00:36:29,538 --> 00:36:31,540
Ibu jadi tak waras.

603
00:36:34,459 --> 00:36:35,419
Ayah...

604
00:36:36,837 --> 00:36:38,130
baik-baik saja?

605
00:36:39,089 --> 00:36:40,257
Mungkin.

606
00:36:43,885 --> 00:36:45,220
Ayahmu berkata

607
00:36:46,179 --> 00:36:48,265
kau kirim uang ke tahanan tiap bulan.

608
00:36:51,393 --> 00:36:52,227
Apa...

609
00:36:54,062 --> 00:36:55,814
Ibu bahagia saat aku sadar?

610
00:36:55,897 --> 00:36:57,649
Tentu saja!

611
00:36:57,941 --> 00:36:59,443
Kami pikir kau sudah mati.

612
00:36:59,568 --> 00:37:02,487
Saat kau koma setahun
bagai neraka bagi kami.

613
00:37:03,238 --> 00:37:06,741
Jika ingat saat itu, ibu sangat takut.

614
00:37:10,495 --> 00:37:11,496
Aku juga bahagia.

615
00:37:14,082 --> 00:37:15,167
Aku sadar,

616
00:37:16,877 --> 00:37:18,295
dan Ibu memelukku.

617
00:37:21,047 --> 00:37:23,091
Ada bau harum dari tubuh Ibu.

618
00:37:26,219 --> 00:37:27,429
Itu kali pertama aku tahu

619
00:37:29,222 --> 00:37:30,432
bahwa bisa ada bau harum

620
00:37:31,433 --> 00:37:32,934
dari tubuh seseorang.

621
00:37:51,786 --> 00:37:52,621
Ibu.

622
00:37:54,706 --> 00:37:55,582
Aku...

623
00:37:58,627 --> 00:38:02,214
sangat senang karena aku anak Ibu.

624
00:38:12,349 --> 00:38:13,517
<i>Aku tahu</i>

625
00:38:14,976 --> 00:38:16,520
<i>aku bukan anak baik untuk Ibu.</i>

626
00:38:20,524 --> 00:38:21,858
Maafkan aku...

627
00:38:26,696 --> 00:38:27,948
karena aku melaporkan Ibu.

628
00:38:30,242 --> 00:38:31,243
Jadi,

629
00:38:33,912 --> 00:38:36,122
tolong jangan begitu lagi.

630
00:38:37,415 --> 00:38:39,125
Maafkan ibu.

631
00:38:41,878 --> 00:38:44,798
Harusnya ibu tak berjudi
walaupun keadaan sulit.

632
00:38:48,677 --> 00:38:50,178
Maafkan ibu, Putraku.

633
00:38:53,598 --> 00:38:54,432
Ibu

634
00:38:56,768 --> 00:38:58,228
payah dan menyedihkan,

635
00:38:58,311 --> 00:39:00,188
ibu bahkan merasa bersalah bicara begini.

636
00:39:04,609 --> 00:39:05,652
Tapi Kang Sin-jae,

637
00:39:06,820 --> 00:39:07,696
kau

638
00:39:09,239 --> 00:39:11,658
adalah keajaiban bagi ibu.

639
00:39:27,215 --> 00:39:28,091
Selamat makan.

640
00:41:06,022 --> 00:41:07,357
<font color="#ffff00">KANTOR KEPOLISIAN SEOUL JONGNO</font>

641
00:41:07,440 --> 00:41:08,733
<i>Bukan aku.</i>

642
00:41:08,817 --> 00:41:10,485
Kenapa aku harus bunuh dia?

643
00:41:11,069 --> 00:41:12,946
Saat aku ke sana, dia sudah mati,

644
00:41:13,238 --> 00:41:16,449
dan darah itu tertempel
saat aku pastikan dia hidup atau mati.

645
00:41:16,533 --> 00:41:17,742
Begitu.

646
00:41:17,826 --> 00:41:20,745
Aku berniat untuk mandi
di rumah teman dan melapor.

647
00:41:20,829 --> 00:41:22,664
- Tapi kau tak lapor.
- Benar.

648
00:41:22,789 --> 00:41:24,249
Kalian tak pernah dalam situasi itu.

649
00:41:25,083 --> 00:41:27,127
Aku tak bisa memikirkan apa-apa.

650
00:41:27,210 --> 00:41:29,921
Dilihat dari pesan,
kau pinjam lima juta won kepada korban.

651
00:41:31,589 --> 00:41:34,342
Kau bunuh dia agar tak perlu bayar?

652
00:41:34,426 --> 00:41:36,177
Ini gila.

653
00:41:37,303 --> 00:41:40,306
Aku telepon dia karena pesan itu,
tapi dia tak jawab.

654
00:41:40,390 --> 00:41:41,558
Jadi, aku ke rumahnya.

655
00:41:41,641 --> 00:41:44,018
Eun-mi tak punya uang sebanyak itu
untuk pinjami aku.

656
00:41:44,227 --> 00:41:46,187
Dia bahkan tak bisa bayar cicilan.

657
00:41:48,189 --> 00:41:50,066
Yang benar saja.

658
00:41:53,069 --> 00:41:55,989
Jang Yeon-ji kini tersangka utama kita.
Mari periksa dia.

659
00:41:56,197 --> 00:41:58,742
Meski menangkapnya,
kita hanya bisa tahan dia 48 jam.

660
00:41:59,325 --> 00:42:00,827
Kita tak punya bukti kuat.

661
00:42:01,035 --> 00:42:02,495
Memang kita punya bukti?

662
00:42:02,620 --> 00:42:03,496
Akan ada bukti.

663
00:42:04,748 --> 00:42:06,583
Aku baca naskah yang Jang Yeon-ji baca.

664
00:42:06,750 --> 00:42:08,918
Cara membunuhnya sama
dengan yang ada di naskah.

665
00:42:09,836 --> 00:42:11,796
Baju berbekas darahnya di bakar di atap.

666
00:42:12,464 --> 00:42:13,423
<i>Judulnya bagus.</i>

667
00:42:14,132 --> 00:42:15,091
<i>Keinginan Magma.</i>

668
00:42:15,175 --> 00:42:18,636
Sepertinya seru.
Judulnya saja sudah buat penasaran.

669
00:42:19,012 --> 00:42:21,097
Telepon siapa itu?

670
00:42:22,182 --> 00:42:23,224
Ya.

671
00:42:31,232 --> 00:42:32,066
Ini Jang Yeon-jin.

672
00:42:33,067 --> 00:42:34,152
Jawab. Cepat.

673
00:42:37,447 --> 00:42:39,073
Halo, aku Letnan Jeong Tae-eul.

674
00:42:45,747 --> 00:42:46,706
Jang Yeon-ji

675
00:42:47,332 --> 00:42:48,333
mau menyerahkan diri.

676
00:42:48,958 --> 00:42:50,043
Astaga.

677
00:42:55,256 --> 00:42:57,759
Pemeriksaan selesai. Silakan masuk.

678
00:42:59,010 --> 00:43:00,970
Akhirnya aku bisa makan makanan ini.

679
00:43:10,730 --> 00:43:11,773
Siap memesan?

680
00:43:12,565 --> 00:43:14,526
Min-hui, bersihkan Meja Tiga.

681
00:43:16,528 --> 00:43:17,779
Isi botol kosong lalu...

682
00:43:18,279 --> 00:43:19,447
Bagin...

683
00:43:31,876 --> 00:43:33,211
Aku

684
00:43:34,254 --> 00:43:36,381
tak bisa makan ini lagi.

685
00:43:37,799 --> 00:43:38,675
Yeong.

686
00:43:39,592 --> 00:43:41,219
Kita harus pergi dari sini.

687
00:43:42,303 --> 00:43:43,263
Ada apa sebenarnya?

688
00:43:44,097 --> 00:43:48,309
Pemilik toko itu mengenali aku dan kau.

689
00:43:49,727 --> 00:43:51,938
Bagaimana orang di dunia ini bisa...

690
00:43:52,021 --> 00:43:53,731
Artinya dia bukan orang dunia ini.

691
00:43:54,983 --> 00:43:57,485
Jika dia kabur, artinya dia kenal kita.

692
00:43:57,569 --> 00:43:58,903
Jika memang begitu,

693
00:44:00,613 --> 00:44:02,073
kau harus tangkap dia.

694
00:44:02,156 --> 00:44:03,199
Bagaimanapun.

695
00:44:04,409 --> 00:44:05,702
Jangan khawatirkan aku.

696
00:44:07,328 --> 00:44:08,413
Baik, Baginda.

697
00:44:16,212 --> 00:44:18,214
Lima orang yang akan membantuku

698
00:44:19,591 --> 00:44:20,883
dalam keadaan apa pun.

699
00:45:18,775 --> 00:45:21,944
<font color="#ffff00">MONARKI KONSTITUSIONAL
DAN KELUARGA KERAJAAN</font>

700
00:45:26,783 --> 00:45:28,326
<font color="#ffff00">PANGERAN GEUM LEE LIM</font>

701
00:45:28,409 --> 00:45:30,411
Payungku pernah tertinggal.

702
00:45:31,120 --> 00:45:32,205
<i>Apa masih ada?</i>

703
00:45:39,045 --> 00:45:40,046
Ini bajumu, 'kan?

704
00:45:40,505 --> 00:45:42,799
Ada bekas darah Ha Eun-mi di sini.

705
00:45:43,299 --> 00:45:45,885
Dan ada sidik jarimu di tong sampah.

706
00:45:47,261 --> 00:45:48,763
Kenapa kau bunuh dia?

707
00:45:50,348 --> 00:45:51,808
Karena aku benci dia.

708
00:45:53,685 --> 00:45:55,561
Kenapa kau kirim pesan ke Park Jung-gu?

709
00:45:57,230 --> 00:45:58,731
Aku juga benci dia.

710
00:46:01,234 --> 00:46:02,735
Kau sudah menyerahkan diri,

711
00:46:03,444 --> 00:46:06,072
dan kau ditangkap
karena membunuh Ha Eun-mi.

712
00:46:13,287 --> 00:46:16,207
<i>Sejak awal aku sudah curiga.</i>

713
00:46:17,208 --> 00:46:19,627
Wanita mengerikan.
Bagaimana bisa dia bunuh temannya?

